---
title: Green Curry
description: Simpler version of Thai green curry perfect for a quick weeknight meal.
---

Heat @coconut-milk{400%ml} in a pan over medium heat.

Stir in @curry-paste{2%tbsp} until it dissolves and becomes fragrant.

Add @vegetable{500%g} (such as bell peppers, carrots, or snap peas) and @tofu{200%g} in cubes, then simmer until the vegetables are tender-crisp.

Season the curry with @fish-sauce{1%tbsp} and @lime-juice{2%tbsp} to your taste.

Garnish with a handful of fresh @basil-leaves{} and serve over steamed rice.
